com.example.symptologger

Class ElasticSearchClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.symptologger.ElasticSearchClient

  • public class ElasticSearchClient
extends java.lang.Object
    ElasticSearchClient represents and handles all interactions with the ElasticSearch server. It creates subclasses that represent specific objects for particular interactions (searching, adding, etc.).
